7, "id": "37", "resolution": "336x188"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0i6-6PySFIQ/hqdefault.jpg", "height": 360, "width": 480, "preference": -7, "id": "38", "resolution": "480x360"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/0i6-6PySFIQ/hqdefault.webp", "preference": -6, "id": "39"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0i6-6PySFIQ/sddefault.jpg", "height": 480, "width": 640, "preference": -5, "id": "40", "resolution": "640x480"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/0i6-6PySFIQ/sddefault.webp", "preference": -4, "id": "41"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0i6-6PySFIQ/hq720.jpg", "preference": -3, "id": "42"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/0i6-6PySFIQ/hq720.webp", "preference": -2, "id": "43"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0i6-6PySFIQ/maxresdefault.jpg", "height": 1080, "width": 1920, "preference": -1, "id": "44", "resolution": "1920x1080"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/0i6-6PySFIQ/maxresdefault.webp", "preference": 0, "id": "45"}], "thumbnail": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0i6-6PySFIQ/maxresdefault.jpg", "description": "Módulo de costos de ContaPyme® y AgroWin® - Tema: Unidades productivas\n\nDescripción:\nComprenda cómo configurar, administrar y costear eficientemente en el sistema ContaPyme/AgroWin sus unidades productivas. Cubrimos los conceptos básicos de costos y explicamos el manejo de los fines productivos con ejemplos según el tipo de empresa o finca. Abordamos el manejo de centros de costos para su costeo y los diferentes tipos de unidades productivas, como órdenes de producción, líneas de producción, cultivos perennes y cultivos transitorios, con un esquema que resume su funcionamiento. Mostramos cómo crear líneas y órdenes de producción en el sistema y cómo definir la estructura de la empresa. Además, resumimos cómo crear cultivos perennes y transitorios en el sistema para empresas agrícolas.\n\nExperta: Ing. Diana María Menjura\nEspecialista en producto de InSoft®\n\nSíganos en nuestras redes sociales:\nFacebook /SoftwareContableContaPyme \nInstagram /contapyme \n\nConozca más en www.contapyme.com y www.agrowin.com", "channel_id": "UCPeasMTjLab3kMBdRvG7vAg", "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCPeasMTjLab3kMBdRvG7vAg", "duration": 1812, "view_count": 103, "age_limit": 0, "webpage_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0i6-6PySFIQ", "categories": ["Education"], "tags": ["Software Contable", "ContaPyme", "Sistema de Facturación", "Contabilidad", "Programa Contable", "NIIF"], "playable_in_embed": true, "live_status": "not_live", "media_type": "video", "_format_sort_fields": ["quality", "res", "fps", "hdr:12", "source", "vcodec", "channels", "acodec", "lang", "proto"], "automatic_captions": {"es-orig": [{"ext": "json3", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/api/timedtext?v=0i6-6PySFIQ&ei=4hgjat68CfChy_sP5523oQw&caps=asr&opi=112496729&xoaf=5&xowf=1&hl=en&ip=0.0.0.0&ipbits=0&expire=1780710226&sparams=ip%2Cipbits%2Cexpire%2Cv%2Cei%2Ccaps%2Copi%2Cxoaf&signature=9D35BB108D8EFE6162E6C56B9EE01DCEE4F92E20.8B755F8FB520B62071865D96C6090518CCC07306&key=yt8&kind=asr&lang=es&fmt=json3", "name": "Spanish (Original)", "impersonate": true}, {"ext": "srv1", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/api/timedtext?v=0i6-6PySFIQ&ei=4hgjat68CfChy_sP5523oQw&caps=asr&opi=112496729&xoaf=5&xowf=1&hl=en&ip=0.0.0.0&ipbits=0&expire=1780710226&sparams=ip%2Cipbits%2Cexpire%2Cv%2Cei%2Ccaps%2Copi%2Cxoaf&signature=9D35BB108D8EFE6162E6C56B9EE01DCEE4F92E20.8B755F8FB520B62071865D96C6090518CCC07306&key=yt8&kind=asr&lang=es&fmt=srv1", "name": "Spanish (Original)", "impersonate": true}, {"ext": "srv2", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/api/timedtext?v=0i6-6PySFIQ&ei=4hgjat68CfChy_sP5523oQw&caps=asr&opi=112496729&xoaf=5&xowf=1&hl=en&ip=0.0.0.0&ipbits=0&expire=1780710226&sparams=ip%2Cipbits%2Cexpire%2Cv%2Cei%2Ccaps%2Copi%2Cxoaf&signature=9D35BB108D8EFE6162E6C56B9EE01DCEE4F92E20.8B755F8FB520B62071865D96C6090518CCC07306&key=yt8&kind=asr&lang=es&fmt=srv2", "name": "Spanish (Original)", "impersonate": true}, {"ext": "srv3", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/api/